      • NurCmdWLANProfile

        public NurCmdWLANProfile(int profileIndex,
                 boolean deleteProfile)
                  throws java.lang.Exception
        Get or delete a WLAN profile by index.
        Parameters:
        profileIndex - The index of the profile to get or delete (0...7).
        deleteProfile - If true then the selected profile is deleted.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - Exception is throewn with invalid profile index i.e. if the index is outside of the range 0...7.
